  "description": "<p>Push your summer camping into shoulder season. Made with the same high-end materials as Therm-a-Rest\u00ae sleeping bags, the Corus -6 \u00b0C Down Quilt packs down small. Hydrophobic down retains less moisture than traditional down and is light and compressible. Elasticized footbox fits over a sleeping pad and perimeter loops let you fasten the quilt in place.</p><ul><li>650 fill-power Nikwax\u00ae hydrophobic down maintains loft, retains 90% less moisture and dries 3 times faster than traditional down</li><li>DWR-treated ripstop polyester shell repels water moisture and condensation</li><li>Box baffle construction maximizes loft and minimizes cool spots</li><li>Full-perimeter side baffles and an elasticized footbox keep cold air out</li><li>SynergyLink\u2122 Connectors kit let you attach it to your Therm-a-Rest mattress for an efficient sleep system</li><li>Includes a stuff sack and a storage sack</li></ul>",
